{"tid":1427231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(新戰線)給攬炒巴及其團隊看看","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:53:23.000Z","uid":62011,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49ea20d86cceb8d3d0c37fc4e566d4fe1e7d7dbc","tid":1427231,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"首先請攬炒巴及其團隊睇下張相 同個post:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dcBvzEg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdcBvzEg.png&h=6be44100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1424603/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1424603/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n8月3日發生黑警除褲<br />\n8月6日民主黨佩諾茜出左封聲明。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/8519-3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speaker.gov%2Fnewsroom%2F8519-3%2F&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75ZxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=ca672e52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/8519-3/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴同團隊們可唔可以出封公開信俾佩諾茜，叫佢就呢件事譴責黑警同說服民主黨通過人權法案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我可以幫手搵6月至今黑警殘酷對待女示威者所有新聞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6e4ae0689f75cd3e2c2449317623052f0da315","tid":1427231,"uid":62011,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"唔一定係公開信，我舉例咋。<br />\n總之傳到去佩諾茜到就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ae44e69f75f99189eb0df14e7a7f514d1d6269","tid":1427231,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf880d93016c9608f50e6b7